Construction/Projects Associate, 1-3PQE, Abu Dhabi
Construction/Projects Associate, 1-3PQE, Abu Dhabi
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
This very highly regarded global law firm is currently recruiting for a 1-3PQE construction/projects associate to be based in the Abu Dhabi office. The ideal candidate will have non-contentious construction experience, have worked on project finance deals and gained experience within an international law firm. You will also speak French and Arabic and already be living in the Middle East, ideally Abu Dhabi.
You will be advising sponsors and lenders on the development of energy, natural resources and other infrastructure projects in the MENA region; and also advising on all manner of project documentation.
